{
  "chapter": 259,
  "chapter_summary": "本章为《寻秦记》第七章\"恶煞临门\"。项少龙在听松别馆与肖月潭密谈，推断出凤菲的情人是韩竭（曹秋道弟子），两人相约私奔。肖月潭警告项少龙韩闯不可信，建议他提防三晋之人，反可信任李园。肖月潭又透露仲孙龙暗中煽动稷下剑手挑衅项少龙。此时费淳来报，五名稷下年轻剑手登门闹事，为首者自称\"快剑\"年常。项少龙以言语折服对方，又展示双匕绝技震慑众人。离开后，肖月潭告知凤菲已从后门离去。金老大追来，告知三天后的稷下剑会上仲孙玄华将挑战项少龙，建议他连夜逃离临淄，但项少龙婉拒，决定去找李园商议。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "有没有办法给我弄一份稷下学宫的地形图？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你要来做什么？曹秋道可不是好惹的。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "我只是去把自己的东西偷回来，齐王将我的百战宝刀赐了给曹秋道，挂在稷下学宫的主堂里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我正想来告诉你这件事，谁说给你知的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙勿要怪我多言，韩闯这人我知之甚深，既好色又贪心，自私自利，为求目的，做事从不讲原则。就算你对他曾有大恩，亦毫无分别。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙万勿松懈下来，你现在只是由一种险恶形势，转到另一种险恶形势里。若我是你，就绝不相信三晋的任何人，反是李园较为可靠，说到底楚人并没有三晋人那么感受到嬴政的威胁。",
      "tone": "语重心长",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "现在我孤身一人，韩闯或龙阳君要对付我还不容易。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你太易信人，首先韩闯等知此事绝不可张扬。若让齐人知道真相，说不定齐王会把你奉为上宾，还恭送你返回咸阳。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "又或者干脆下毒手杀你灭口，这事谁都不能确定。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "秘密杀了我又谁会知道呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "起码会有李园知道，韩闯和龙阳君岂无顾忌。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "要杀你是那么容易吗？谁不知项少龙剑法盖世，而且一旦让你走脱，这里又非三晋地头，哪个人有把握可再度擒杀你？若我是他们，首先要教你绝不起疑，然后把你引进无路可逃的绝境，再以卑鄙手段，教你在有力难施下中伏身亡。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "我会小心。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "或者是我多虑吧！但小心点总是好的。照理龙阳君已害了你一次，很难再狠下心肠下第二次手。但人心难测，尤其牵涉到国家和族人的利害，少龙好好想想。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "在这里老哥你是我唯一完全信任的人，凤菲的问题现在更是复杂。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我虽不认识韩竭，但观他不远千里往咸阳追求荣华富贵，真肯为了个女人放弃一切吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "据说韩竭乃韩国的贵族，在韩时早和嫪毐认识，既肯和嫪毐这种人相交，很难会是个好人，若他是骗凤菲而非爱凤菲，问题将更严重。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这种事我们做外人的很难明白，凤菲确是那种可使男人肯牺牲一切的女人。少龙不妨一试，好过白白便宜韩竭。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "知道她的情郎是韩竭，我更不会碰她。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我想到哩！凤菲必是打算潜返咸阳做韩竭的秘密情人，而此事已得嫪毐首肯，只是要瞒过吕不韦。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "凤菲真个狡猾，当日我告诉她说张泉背后的主子是吕不韦时，她还装出震骇不已、慌惶失措的姿态表情，骗得我死心塌地，原来我竟是给她玩弄于股掌之上。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我还探听到另一件会使你头痛的事，你要知道吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "我早麻木了，说出来亦不会有太大的不安。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "仲孙何忌照我的话去找仲孙龙打听消息，原来这吸血鬼暗中派人通知稷下那班狂人，说你自恃剑法高明，不把齐国剑手看在眼内。唉！这人如此卑鄙，因怕开罪李园和解子元，故此在暗里使卑鄙手段。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "早有人来找过我，还吃了暗亏。若是明刀明枪，倒没什么可怕的，总不会是曹秋道亲来找我吧！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你要小心麻承甲和闵廷章这两个人，他们虽爱惹是生非，一副唯恐天下不乱的性子，但确有真实本领。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_chun",
      "speaker_name": "费淳",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "管事不好了，有群剑手凶神恶煞的来到，指名道姓地要见管事。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "高壮青年",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "来人可是自夸剑术无双的狗奴才沈良。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这位公子高姓大名，为何一出言便犯下两个错误？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nian_chang",
      "speaker_name": "年常",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "行不改姓，坐不改名，'快剑'年常就是本公子，我犯的是什么错？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_nian_chang",
      "text": "首先我从没有认为自己的剑术有什么了得，其次我更不是狗奴才。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "矮壮青年",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "歌姬的下人，不是狗奴才是什么东西？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "剑手",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "叫你的主子来求情，我们就放过你。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来替人办事的就是狗奴才，那齐国内除大王外，不都是狗奴才吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kun_shan",
      "speaker_name": "昆山",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "小人早说必是有人中伤沈管事哩！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nian_chang",
      "speaker_name": "年常",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "横竖我们来了，总不能教我们白走一趟，沈管事露一手吧！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_nian_chang",
      "text": "这个容易，沈某的剑法虽不堪入五位大家之眼，但却有手小玩意，看刀！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沈某尚有要事办理，不送了！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙真懂齐人爱面子的心态，这么一来，这五个小子哪敢说出真话，只会扬言你向他们认错，弄到谁都再没兴趣来找你。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "仲孙龙既是爱面子的齐人，怎肯罢休。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你今天找得李园出马，仲孙龙怎都要忍这口气的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "知否刚才凤菲和小屏儿在几个心腹家将护送下由后门离开呢？",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "你怎知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "云娘见到嘛！是她告诉我的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "会否是去见韩竭？我若可跟踪她就好了。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你在这里人地生疏，不给人发现才怪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "金老大",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "沈管事留步。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 255,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "金老大",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "沈管事有没有空说几句话？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "老哥记得给我弄稷下学宫的地形图，我会自行到李园处。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "金老大",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "沈兄！你今趟很麻烦呢！",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "text": "我的麻烦多不胜数，何妨再多一件。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "金老大",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "沈兄果是英雄好汉，我金老大没交错你这朋友。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "text": "金老大才真够朋友，究竟是什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "金老大",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "昨晚田单为吕不韦举行洗尘宴，我和素芳都有参加，我恰好与仲孙龙的一个手下同席，闲聊中他问我是否认识你，我当然不会透露我们间的真正关系。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "text": "不是悬赏要取我项上的人头吧！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "金老大",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "沈兄真看得开，但尚未严重至这个地步，你听过'稷下剑会'这件事吗？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "金老大",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "每月初一，稷下学宫都举行骑射大会，让后起之秀有显露身手的机会，今天是廿七，三天后就是下月的剑会，照例他们会邀请一些宾客参加。嘿！那只是客气的说法，不好听点就是找人来比试。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "text": "若他们要我参加，我大可托病推辞，总不能硬将我押去吧！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "金老大",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这些邀请信均是通过齐王发出来的，沈兄够胆不给齐王面子吗？听说仲孙龙的儿子仲孙玄华对沈兄震怒非常，决定亲身下场教训你。他虽不敢杀人，用的也只是木剑，但凭他的剑力，要打断沈兄的一条腿绝非难事。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "金老大",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "沈兄不若夤夜离开临淄，凤小姐必不会怪你。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "金老大",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "仲孙龙势力在此如日中天，连有身份地位的公卿大臣也畏之如虎，沈兄怎都斗他不过的。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_da",
      "text": "多谢老大的提点，这事我或有应付之法。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 259,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    }
  ],
